22
00:01:44,714 --> 00:01:46,774
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Akina's Eight-Six?!</b></font>

23
00:01:54,454 --> 00:01:56,124
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Did you see that, big brother?!</b></font>

24
00:01:56,124 --> 00:01:58,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah. I guess...</b></font>

25
00:01:58,794 --> 00:02:02,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...Kyoichi is scheming behind the scenes.</b></font>

26
00:02:02,194 --> 00:02:05,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Can we let him race the Emperor?</b></font>

27
00:02:05,234 --> 00:02:09,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>There's no way he can pull it off this time!</b></font>

28
00:02:09,074 --> 00:02:11,174
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This is street racing.</b></font>

29
00:02:11,174 --> 00:02:13,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's not up to us to decide</b></font>

30
00:02:13,074 --> 00:02:15,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>who gets to race whom.</b></font>

31
00:02:15,414 --> 00:02:17,604
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But, big brother...</b></font>

32
00:02:27,394 --> 00:02:29,894
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>In the race I saw,</b></font>

33
00:02:29,894 --> 00:02:32,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>he totally exceeded my expectations.</b></font>

34
00:02:31,824 --> 00:02:42,104
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}"Fujiwara Tofu Shop"</b></font>

35
00:02:32,464 --> 00:02:34,634
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I can't believe he's only 18.</b></font>

36
00:02:34,634 --> 00:02:35,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Come on, now.</b></font>

37
00:02:35,864 --> 00:02:39,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>When I was 18, I was far
more capable than that.</b></font>

38
00:02:39,234 --> 00:02:42,764
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You may be the only one who thinks so.</b></font>

39
00:02:44,074 --> 00:02:48,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yuichi says your son is more talented than you.</b></font>

40
00:02:48,074 --> 00:02:51,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He says you just don't want
to accept your son's talent</b></font>

41
00:02:51,314 --> 00:02:53,904
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>because you're so stubborn.</b></font>

42
00:02:57,784 --> 00:03:00,724
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Anyway, when he exceeds his limits,</b></font>

43
00:03:00,724 --> 00:03:02,324
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>so will the engine.</b></font>

44
00:03:02,324 --> 00:03:05,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Sooner or later, it'll blow.</b></font>

45
00:03:05,394 --> 00:03:08,424
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Can he keep winning until then?</b></font>

46
00:03:10,734 --> 00:03:12,754
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Who knows?</b></font>

47
00:03:29,684 --> 00:03:32,524
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Here's the Eight-Six.</b></font>

48
00:03:32,524 --> 00:03:35,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He took the bait as expected.</b></font>

49
00:03:42,394 --> 00:03:45,424
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Thank you for showing up.</b></font>

50
00:03:46,804 --> 00:03:50,134
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>As promised, I'll be your opponent.</b></font>

51
00:03:50,134 --> 00:03:53,904
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's the least I can do for your trouble.</b></font>

52
00:03:55,374 --> 00:03:57,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But I won't take it easy.</b></font>

53
00:03:57,914 --> 00:04:01,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>My courtesy to you is to give it my best.</b></font>

54
00:04:08,654 --> 00:04:10,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>His attitude is different.</i></b></font>

55
00:04:10,994 --> 00:04:14,434
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>He looks like a different person.</i></b></font>

56
00:04:14,434 --> 00:04:19,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Let's go. We'll use the
"Handicap" method like before.</b></font>

57
00:04:21,004 --> 00:04:22,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You go first.</b></font>

58
00:04:22,834 --> 00:04:26,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The race starts after the first corner.</b></font>

59
00:04:32,884 --> 00:04:36,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>See you later. Call me if you need me.</b></font>

60
00:04:36,554 --> 00:04:38,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah.</b></font>

61
00:04:51,434 --> 00:04:54,734
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Something's gonna happen tonight.</i></b></font>

62
00:04:56,274 --> 00:04:59,204
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I have this uneasy feeling.</i></b></font>

63
00:05:06,984 --> 00:05:10,084
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The Emperors came to rile up Takumi?!</b></font>

64
00:05:10,084 --> 00:05:12,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>They showed up here?</b></font>

65
00:05:12,554 --> 00:05:16,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I bet they really regret
losing to Takumi in Akina.</b></font>

66
00:05:16,394 --> 00:05:22,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>After all, they came to Gunma
planning to sweep the area.</b></font>

67
00:05:22,834 --> 00:05:25,434
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What did Takumi say?</b></font>

68
00:05:25,434 --> 00:05:27,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He's not interested.</b></font>

69
00:05:27,504 --> 00:05:29,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's good.</b></font>

70
00:05:29,674 --> 00:05:31,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He has no reason to go to Akagi</b></font>

71
00:05:31,504 --> 00:05:35,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>and battle it out with that monstrous Lan-Evo.</b></font>

72
00:05:35,214 --> 00:05:37,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yes.</b></font>

73
00:05:37,544 --> 00:05:40,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Okay, I see.</b></font>

74
00:05:42,954 --> 00:05:44,624
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This is weird.</b></font>

75
00:05:44,624 --> 00:05:46,124
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What's wrong, Itsuki?</b></font>

76
00:05:46,124 --> 00:05:48,124
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Takumi isn't home.</b></font>

77
00:05:48,124 --> 00:05:51,294
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He got a phone call, and then he just took off.</b></font>

78
00:05:51,294 --> 00:05:52,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>A phone call?</b></font>

79
00:05:52,464 --> 00:05:56,134
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I forgot to set my VCR to tape a show tonight,</b></font>

80
00:05:56,134 --> 00:05:59,534
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>so I wanted to ask him to tape it for me.</b></font>

81
00:05:59,534 --> 00:06:01,204
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Did he take the car?</b></font>

82
00:06:01,204 --> 00:06:03,634
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I think so.</b></font>

83
00:06:03,634 --> 00:06:06,204
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I know! He has a date!</b></font>

84
00:06:06,204 --> 00:06:08,174
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>With that girl.</b></font>

85
00:06:08,174 --> 00:06:10,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Natsuki Mogi?</b></font>

86
00:06:10,514 --> 00:06:13,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's her. I'm positive.</b></font>

87
00:06:13,544 --> 00:06:15,884
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I envy him.</b></font>

88
00:06:15,884 --> 00:06:18,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If I had a cute girl like that,</b></font>

89
00:06:18,154 --> 00:06:21,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I wouldn't be killing time here with you.</b></font>

90
00:06:21,224 --> 00:06:24,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What are you saying, Kenji?!</b></font>

91
00:06:24,064 --> 00:06:26,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We racers don't need girls!</b></font>

92
00:06:26,394 --> 00:06:29,334
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--Right, Iketani?
--Right!</b></font>

93
00:06:29,334 --> 00:06:31,524
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>They're pathetic!</i></b></font>

94
00:06:47,384 --> 00:06:51,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I want you to know that I
don't consider this a race.</b></font>

95
00:06:52,454 --> 00:06:58,424
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm going to teach you the
difference between a fun car...</b></font>

96
00:06:58,424 --> 00:07:00,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...and a fast car.</b></font>

97
00:07:00,464 --> 00:07:02,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This is a seminar.</b></font>

98
00:07:11,804 --> 00:07:13,904
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm ready.</b></font>

99
00:07:19,214 --> 00:07:20,974
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>There he goes!</b></font>

100
00:07:29,024 --> 00:07:32,494
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Go get him, Kyoichi!</b></font>

101
00:07:32,494 --> 00:07:35,894
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>This is hard for me to comprehend.</i></b></font>

102
00:07:35,894 --> 00:07:38,534
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>He intentionally threw himself</i></b></font>

103
00:07:38,534 --> 00:07:41,094
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>into this unevenly matched race.</i></b></font>

104
00:07:44,704 --> 00:07:46,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>How can an obsolete Eight-Six</i></b></font>

105
00:07:46,374 --> 00:07:51,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>defeat Kyoichi's perfectly tuned Evo III?</i></b></font>

106
00:07:51,044 --> 00:07:53,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>And this isn't Akina, either.</i></b></font>

107
00:07:53,344 --> 00:07:58,084
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Is that guy too stupid to realize that?</i></b></font>

108
00:07:58,084 --> 00:08:01,654
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Does he trust his instincts</i>
<i>and experience that much?</i></b></font>

109
00:08:01,654 --> 00:08:04,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I don't understand what he's thinking.</i></b></font>

110
00:08:09,034 --> 00:08:13,734
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Or does he believe he</i>
<i>actually has a chance to win?</i></b></font>

111
00:08:15,474 --> 00:08:17,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Maybe he is...</i></b></font>

112
00:08:19,504 --> 00:08:23,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>...a racing genius in the making!</i></b></font>

113
00:08:46,904 --> 00:08:50,164
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Unbelievable! They're really racing!</b></font>

114
00:08:54,414 --> 00:08:56,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Watch me, Ryosuke.</i></b></font>

115
00:08:56,674 --> 00:08:59,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>4WD cars can't lose to 2WD cars.</i></b></font>

116
00:09:02,054 --> 00:09:06,684
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>This race also serves as a</i>
<i>challenge sent out to you.</i></b></font>

117
00:09:11,524 --> 00:09:14,824
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Watch out! He's swinging wide!</b></font>

118
00:09:37,584 --> 00:09:39,884
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That Eight-Six is amazing!</b></font>

119
00:09:39,884 --> 00:09:44,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He was just inches from
that vine-covered guardrail!</b></font>

120
00:09:44,224 --> 00:09:46,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Is he insane?!</b></font>

121
00:09:46,064 --> 00:09:48,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Even Akagi racers don't
attack that corner like that!</b></font>

122
00:09:58,004 --> 00:10:03,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Big brother... the Evo III's noisy
backfire didn't sound normal.</b></font>

123
00:10:03,614 --> 00:10:05,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I noticed that, too.</b></font>

124
00:10:05,714 --> 00:10:08,854
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That Evo III has the same system</b></font>

125
00:10:08,854 --> 00:10:11,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>that a WRC rally car has.</b></font>

126
00:10:12,584 --> 00:10:15,724
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The misfiring system!</b></font>

127
00:10:15,724 --> 00:10:18,894
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's a good strategy by Kyoichi.</b></font>

128
00:10:18,894 --> 00:10:21,894
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's the best system imaginable</b></font>

129
00:10:21,894 --> 00:10:25,304
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>for a turbo car on a downhill course.</b></font>

130
00:10:25,304 --> 00:10:27,304
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Akagi's slope is much more severe</b></font>

131
00:10:27,304 --> 00:10:29,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>than those of Akina and Myogi.</b></font>

132
00:10:29,874 --> 00:10:32,204
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Right after the start is a low-speed section</b></font>

133
00:10:32,204 --> 00:10:34,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>where they go straight down the hill</b></font>

134
00:10:34,544 --> 00:10:37,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>in a short amount of time.</b></font>

135
00:10:37,614 --> 00:10:40,754
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Controlling the braking and steering</b></font>

136
00:10:40,754 --> 00:10:43,084
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>rather than abusing the power is the key.</b></font>

137
00:10:45,624 --> 00:10:48,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He developed his technique
in the Gymkhana circuit,</b></font>

138
00:10:48,794 --> 00:10:51,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>so he's exceptional at slow corners.</b></font>

139
00:10:54,464 --> 00:10:57,294
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He certainly has better technique now</b></font>

140
00:10:57,294 --> 00:11:00,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>than he did a year ago.</b></font>

141
00:11:00,464 --> 00:11:03,924
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This new Kyoichi is a tough opponent.</b></font>

142
00:11:08,544 --> 00:11:12,744
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>The belief that 4WD cars can't turn is obsolete.</i></b></font>

143
00:11:15,754 --> 00:11:18,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>My Evo III can turn!</i></b></font>

144
00:11:51,154 --> 00:11:55,424
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I'm being hunted down... like helpless prey.</i></b></font>

145
00:12:00,894 --> 00:12:03,534
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The Evo III sure is fast!</b></font>

146
00:12:03,534 --> 00:12:06,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It even challenges the Eight-Six at the corners.</b></font>

147
00:12:06,404 --> 00:12:09,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>A better car or better skill?</b></font>

148
00:12:09,074 --> 00:12:12,764
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's both! Sudo's cornering is unreal!</b></font>

149
00:12:16,544 --> 00:12:20,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You know how Kyoichi Sudo races, right?</b></font>

150
00:12:20,214 --> 00:12:21,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What's his style?</b></font>

151
00:12:21,554 --> 00:12:25,284
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He never makes mistakes.</b></font>

152
00:12:25,284 --> 00:12:28,454
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He sticks with the basics
and avoids flashy moves.</b></font>

153
00:12:28,454 --> 00:12:32,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>In a race, he patiently tests
his opponent's weaknesses.</b></font>

154
00:12:32,464 --> 00:12:37,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He will choose the most rational way to win.</b></font>

155
00:12:37,234 --> 00:12:40,434
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He won't self-destruct, then.</b></font>

156
00:12:40,434 --> 00:12:42,934
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He's different from Seiji.</b></font>

157
00:12:42,934 --> 00:12:46,104
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Rationality is Kyoichi's bible.</b></font>

158
00:12:46,104 --> 00:12:50,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's why he's only interested in 4WD cars.</b></font>

159
00:12:50,984 --> 00:12:54,284
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Against an equally skilled opponent,
he'll make sure his car</b></font>

160
00:12:54,284 --> 00:12:56,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>is better-equipped to win the race.</b></font>

161
00:12:56,614 --> 00:12:58,884
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He's like that.</b></font>

162
00:12:58,884 --> 00:13:02,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You sound rather bitter.</b></font>

163
00:13:02,394 --> 00:13:05,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I dislike him.</b></font>

164
00:13:05,024 --> 00:13:07,754
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I certainly don't want to lose to him.</b></font>

165
00:13:16,674 --> 00:13:20,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>That firing sound is so noisy!</i></b></font>

166
00:13:23,074 --> 00:13:25,274
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I can't stand it!</i></b></font>

167
00:13:34,794 --> 00:13:38,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>His adaptability is exceptional.</i></b></font>

168
00:13:38,694 --> 00:13:41,964
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>He has no prior experience on this course.</i></b></font>

169
00:13:43,634 --> 00:13:47,604
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>But he can still race at this pace.</i></b></font>

170
00:13:47,604 --> 00:13:50,634
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>What an unbelievable "downhill" sense.</i></b></font>

171
00:13:50,634 --> 00:13:53,644
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>But no more playing around.</i></b></font>

172
00:13:53,644 --> 00:13:55,944
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I'll end this shortly.</i></b></font>

173
00:14:02,554 --> 00:14:04,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Thank you very much!</b></font>

174
00:14:10,394 --> 00:14:12,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Mogi?</b></font>

175
00:14:14,734 --> 00:14:17,334
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Takumi's girlfriend?</b></font>

176
00:14:17,334 --> 00:14:19,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I got you something.</b></font>

177
00:14:19,234 --> 00:14:22,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Thank you so much!</b></font>

178
00:14:22,034 --> 00:14:23,934
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm happy.</b></font>

179
00:14:23,934 --> 00:14:25,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Where is Takumi?</b></font>

180
00:14:25,374 --> 00:14:28,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>His shift ended at 5:00 today.</b></font>

181
00:14:28,374 --> 00:14:30,574
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You haven't seen him?</b></font>

182
00:14:30,574 --> 00:14:32,584
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No.</b></font>

183
00:14:32,584 --> 00:14:36,584
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I thought you were with him.</b></font>

184
00:14:36,584 --> 00:14:40,254
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>There it is, my favorite cheesecake!</b></font>

185
00:14:40,254 --> 00:14:42,424
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Bon appétit!</b></font>

186
00:14:42,424 --> 00:14:47,084
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If Takumi isn't on a date, where did he go?</b></font>

187
00:14:48,594 --> 00:14:51,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You said he took the Eight-Six, right?</b></font>

188
00:14:51,464 --> 00:14:53,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah.</b></font>

189
00:14:53,364 --> 00:14:56,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He may have taken the Emperors' bait</b></font>

190
00:14:56,474 --> 00:14:58,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>and gone to Akagi.</b></font>

191
00:14:58,474 --> 00:15:00,134
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No way!</b></font>

192
00:15:07,044 --> 00:15:09,884
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Takumi went to Akagi?</i></b></font>

193
00:15:31,504 --> 00:15:36,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>We're entering the flatter,</i>
<i>mid-speed section here.</i></b></font>

194
00:15:36,244 --> 00:15:39,904
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Without a slope, he's as slow as a turtle.</i></b></font>

195
00:15:54,634 --> 00:15:56,894
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>The next "S" turn will do.</i></b></font>

196
00:15:56,894 --> 00:15:59,964
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>He can't avoid my counterattack.</i></b></font>

197
00:16:02,634 --> 00:16:04,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>There!</b></font>

198
00:16:09,344 --> 00:16:10,844
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>No way!</i></b></font>

199
00:16:10,844 --> 00:16:14,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>This is a short, full-blast section.</i></b></font>

200
00:16:14,554 --> 00:16:16,644
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>What acceleration!</i></b></font>

201
00:16:21,854 --> 00:16:24,764
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>He's charging in from the outside.</i></b></font>

202
00:16:24,764 --> 00:16:28,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Challenging the Eight-Six at a corner?!</i></b></font>

203
00:16:34,574 --> 00:16:38,334
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>He'll take the inside</i>
<i>position at the next corner.</i></b></font>

204
00:16:43,074 --> 00:16:47,284
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>And with that amazing acceleration...</i></b></font>

205
00:16:47,284 --> 00:16:49,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>...the Eight-Six is going down!</i></b></font>

206
00:16:58,694 --> 00:17:01,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What?! The Evo III took the lead?</b></font>

207
00:17:01,564 --> 00:17:04,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>At a corner?</b></font>

208
00:17:04,034 --> 00:17:05,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah...</b></font>

209
00:17:05,864 --> 00:17:08,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah.</b></font>

210
00:17:08,034 --> 00:17:10,524
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah. I see.</b></font>

211
00:17:13,704 --> 00:17:15,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Big brother?</b></font>

212
00:17:15,714 --> 00:17:18,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's just like Kyoichi.</b></font>

213
00:17:18,044 --> 00:17:22,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He chose not to attack
at the steep-slope section.</b></font>

214
00:17:22,054 --> 00:17:25,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He waited until the Eight-Six
lost speed on the flatter section.</b></font>

215
00:17:25,984 --> 00:17:29,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>With his technique and the Evo III's abilities,</b></font>

216
00:17:29,154 --> 00:17:31,324
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Kyoichi could've taken the lead earlier.</b></font>

217
00:17:31,324 --> 00:17:35,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But he waited until he had
a surefire chance to pass.</b></font>

218
00:17:35,994 --> 00:17:38,434
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's the Kyoichi I know.</b></font>

219
00:17:38,434 --> 00:17:42,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Will the Eight-Six have a
chance to regain the lead?</b></font>

220
00:17:42,874 --> 00:17:45,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Don't ask me that.</b></font>

221
00:17:45,544 --> 00:17:49,204
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I know you can figure out the answer yourself.</b></font>

222
00:18:04,524 --> 00:18:06,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Idiot!</b></font>

223
00:18:06,364 --> 00:18:10,534
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He should've stayed home and let us handle it!</b></font>

224
00:18:10,534 --> 00:18:14,624
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He didn't have to suffer this pointless loss!</b></font>

225
00:18:50,404 --> 00:18:52,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>He's following me...</i></b></font>

226
00:18:52,074 --> 00:18:54,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>...at the same distance.</i></b></font>

227
00:18:54,714 --> 00:18:59,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Amazing! He picked up more</i>
<i>speed after losing the lead.</i></b></font>

228
00:19:03,354 --> 00:19:07,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Usually, the corner exit
is the key for a turbo car</b></font>

229
00:19:07,184 --> 00:19:09,524
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>while it's the corner entrance for an NA.</b></font>

230
00:19:09,524 --> 00:19:14,124
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>To put it simply, that's the
theory of downhill racing.</b></font>

231
00:19:14,124 --> 00:19:18,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But with the misfiring system...</b></font>

232
00:19:18,364 --> 00:19:21,204
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Right. The misfiring system makes</b></font>

233
00:19:21,204 --> 00:19:26,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>both the Turbo's torque and
the NA's response possible.</b></font>

234
00:19:26,044 --> 00:19:27,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>With Kyoichi's abilities,</b></font>

235
00:19:27,374 --> 00:19:31,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>that Evo III becomes a
monstrous cornering machine.</b></font>

236
00:19:31,384 --> 00:19:34,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It can superbly enter and exit a corner.</b></font>

237
00:19:34,384 --> 00:19:36,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's perfect for a dogfight.</b></font>

238
00:19:38,384 --> 00:19:40,884
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Like I said, this race was suicide!</b></font>

239
00:19:40,884 --> 00:19:45,094
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>From the get-go, this race
was never about speed.</b></font>

240
00:19:45,094 --> 00:19:46,684
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What?</b></font>

241
00:19:49,894 --> 00:19:51,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Think about it.</b></font>

242
00:19:51,404 --> 00:19:54,574
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Kyoichi has carefully studied this course,</b></font>

243
00:19:54,574 --> 00:19:58,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>while Takumi Fujiwara has no experience here.</b></font>

244
00:19:58,074 --> 00:20:01,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>There's no question who the favorite is.</b></font>

245
00:20:01,074 --> 00:20:02,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Right.</b></font>

246
00:20:04,274 --> 00:20:07,784
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I don't know what went on between them,</b></font>

247
00:20:07,784 --> 00:20:09,454
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but Fujiwara showed up</b></font>

248
00:20:09,454 --> 00:20:13,084
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>without the tools to win this race.</b></font>

249
00:20:13,084 --> 00:20:17,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But why did he have to be so irrational?</b></font>

250
00:20:17,554 --> 00:20:20,724
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Only he understands that.</b></font>

251
00:20:20,724 --> 00:20:22,734
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Sometimes we want to race</b></font>

252
00:20:22,734 --> 00:20:25,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>to blow off some frustration within us.</b></font>

253
00:20:27,734 --> 00:20:30,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He had that air about him.</b></font>

254
00:20:36,314 --> 00:20:38,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This isn't his normal racing style.</b></font>

255
00:20:38,914 --> 00:20:42,744
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The Eight-Six's high-pitched
exhaust sounds like...</b></font>

256
00:20:45,254 --> 00:20:47,484
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...an enraged roar.</b></font>

257
00:21:19,384 --> 00:21:24,294
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Whenever I turned around</i></b></font>

258
00:21:24,294 --> 00:21:29,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>There was always that</i>
<i>unchanging smile of yours</i></b></font>

259
00:21:29,564 --> 00:21:34,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>It was there on days when</i>
<i>I was too tired to go on</i></b></font>

260
00:21:34,234 --> 00:21:43,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>And even on days with a little happiness in them</i></b></font>

261
00:21:43,044 --> 00:21:51,624
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>My hands aren't enough</i></b></font>

262
00:21:51,624 --> 00:21:58,724
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>To hold on to all the love you gave me</i></b></font>

263
00:22:00,724 --> 00:22:07,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>The warm wind</i></b></font>

264
00:22:07,864 --> 00:22:15,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Comes back quietly and tenderly</i></b></font>

265
00:22:15,544 --> 00:22:23,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>And as I gaze at the sky alone</i></b></font>

266
00:22:23,554 --> 00:22:30,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>You smile down upon me</i></b></font>

267
00:22:30,794 --> 00:22:38,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>You are still waving to me from the radiant light</i></b></font>

268
00:22:38,704 --> 00:22:48,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Just like you did that day</i></b></font>

269
00:22:51,384 --> 00:22:57,084
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>You are my everlasting memory</i></b></font>

270
00:23:04,194 --> 00:23:06,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Takumi gave up the lead.</i></b></font>

271
00:23:06,064 --> 00:23:09,934
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Can he ever regain the lead, and...?</i></b></font>

272
00:23:09,934 --> 00:23:12,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Next on Initial D: Second Stage...</i></b></font>

273
00:23:12,504 --> 00:23:14,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>"Goodbye Eight-Six."</i></b></font>

274
00:23:14,004 --> 00:23:15,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Don't miss it!</i></b></font>

